OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBlue Monday: Samaritans on 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhand at railway stations   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Samaritans volunteers hope to debunk   
OL,6, the myth of "Blue Monday" by handing   
OL,7, out free tea bags at railway stations  
OL,8, across the West and South West.        
OL,10,FThe charity opposes applying that      
OL,11,Fphrase to the third Monday in January, 
OL,12,Foften referred to as the toughest day  
OL,13,Fof the year.                           
OL,15,FInstead it has launched what it is     
OL,16,Fcalling "Brew Monday".                 
OL,18,FThe idea is to encourage people to feel
OL,19,Fable to take about issues such as      
OL,20,Fmental health and loneliness.          
